Customer: Hello.

Customer: Sir, Sakshi baat kar rahi thi.
Executive: Yes from Andhra Pradesh.
Customer: Yes, I am from IndiaMART actually.
Customer: Sir, main ye keh rahi thi aap Anirudh apne account manager ko call kyun nahi karte ho sir?
Executive: Unko call kiya uske baad five minutes baad aur ek madam baat karke aapka ye number diya hai nahi mere paas aapke paas phone karke number dene ke liye bole.
Customer: Number kiska number sir?
Executive: Seller seller seller seller ka number.
Customer: Seller ka number kaun dega aapko? Kaun se seller ka number chahiye?
Executive: Oil.
Customer: Nahi, aapko kiska number chahiye?
Executive: We are from we are from Arogya.
Customer: I know sir, you are from Arogya but main ye puch rahi hu aapko kiska number chahiye?
Executive: We are we request seller seller seller seller company number, company ka number.
Customer: Sir, actually we are not getting your point. Aapko seller ka number chahiye agar to aapko unse baat karni padegi na buyer se. Matlab aapko product sell karna hai aur buy karna hai?
Executive: Sell karna hai.
Customer: Sell karna hai na? To aapko apne buyer ka number chahiye. To uska link to Anirudh aapke account manager aapko share kar rahe hain na whatsapp pe?
Executive: Kar rahe hain, buyer seller ka link nahi aa raha hai.
Customer: Sir, actually Anirudh already sharing link whatsapp pe aap unko consume bhi nahi kar rahe ho.
Executive: Nahi nahi, wo seller lekin pura number buyer number aa raha hai seller number nahi aa raha hai.
Customer: Sir, seller number nahi aata hai. Hum aapko buylead dete hain aap consume karte hain waha pe buyer ka number aata hai aap unko call karte hain. Number nahi dikhega aapko. Link dikhega. Pehle aapko buylead consume karni padegi.
Customer: There is a process.
Executive: English or Hindi?
Customer: Hindi bolo.
Customer: Hindi. To main ye keh rahi hu sir ki jo link aapko bheja jata hai aur jo IndiaMART ki application pe jo dikhta hai na aapko buyer ki details supplier ki basically aap un pe aapko consume buylead click karna padta hai. Jab aap buylead pe click karoge aur tab uske baad buyer ki details aayengi tab aap unko call kar paoge. Hum number nahi dete.
Executive: Accha aisa hai.
Customer: Haan ji. Aur isi ke regarding isi ke regarding aapko ek cheez ye bhi batani thi mujhe koi bhi concern koi bhi discussion ho na to aap please apne account manager ko call kara kariye kyunki aapko zyada acche se wahi guide kar payenge.
Executive: Accha.
Customer: Customer kehte hain tab call kariye jab aapke account manager aapko support na kar rahe ho.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Haan ji, aapke paas number hai Anirudh ji ka?
Executive: Hai hai hai.
Customer: Ji, abhi aapka issue resolve ho gaya hai ya kuch aur bhi puchna hai aapko sir?
Executive: Nahi nahi, abhi main buyer ko ye click karna hai nahi click karne ke baad number aayega.
Customer: Haan, link pe aap click karoge click karne ke baad aapko sari details buyer ki dikh jayengi ki kya product hai kya price hai kya quantity hai. Agar aap usko lena chahte ho product ko buyer se baat karna chahte ho to niche consume buyer likha hoga. Us pe aap click karoge click karne ke baad aapko buyer ki details aa jayengi matlab ki unka number aur email id jo bhi hoga waha pe.
Executive: Accha seller ko aisa aayega.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Accha aisa hai.
Customer: Ji, bas itna hi puchna tha?
